channel.title: Help with making my server go online please!
channel.description: Ok so I just got back into Rsps's and i used to host all the time... But i try to host my server again and it just isn't working!! I have port-forwarded and it even says the server is online but im getting an Error connecting to server?? Please can someone help over TeamViewer or something!! I have all the ips changed to my no-ip and there is nothing blocking anything.. I just don't understand why i get this error http://gyazo.com/845def6710c79be18f6d18ff7500af2f Someone please help!!!
